strapiSongs.title: Drawing Down the Moon (The Art of the Cunning)
strapiSongs.credits: Music by Victor Fisher of Reenchantment.
strapiSongs.description: This soundscape is a journey into the secrets of witchcraft. It was recorded with the bassoon and the tin whistle, along with various synthesized tones.
